text: Neochodaeus is a genus of sand-loving scarab beetles in the family Ochodaeidae. There are at least four described species in Neochodaeus. ==Species== * Neochodaeus frontalis (LeConte, 1863) * Neochodaeus praesidii (Bates, 1887) * Neochodaeus repandus (Fall, 1909) * Neochodaeus striatus (LeConte, 1854) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * Category:scarabaeiformia
